OL,3,GOPINIONCLive announcers: an essential
OL,4,Cpart of PSB channels
OL,5,
OL,6,FOccasionally there was no form of
OL,7,Fbuffer before an imported programme or
OL,8,Ffilm. It looked messy and I can't
OL,9,Fimagine the IBA exactly approved even
OL,10,Fif this practice wasn't specifically
OL,11,Fprohibited.
OL,13,FFor the same reason, some ITV regions
OL,14,Flooked a little messy initially after
OL,15,Fproduction company idents were
OL,16,Fwithdrawn in 1988.
OL,18,FSoon most regions realised how this
OL,19,Flooked and a local ident or in-vision
OL,20,Fannouncement before each programme
OL,21,Fbecame the norm in almost every region.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
