OL,3,GOPINIONCLive announcers: an essential
OL,4,Cpart of PSB channels
OL,5,
OL,6,FSome programmes benefit from a nicely
OL,7,Fscripted introduction. In the case of a
OL,8,Fchannel like BBC One, the feeling that
OL,9,Fa live announcer is watching live with
OL,10,Fthe audience helps to lift the channel
OL,11,Fabove the others. The channel is a
OL,12,Fliving, breathing, reactive thing ` not
OL,13,Fa streamed video.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
