OL,3,GOPINIONCLive announcers: an essential
OL,4,Cpart of PSB channels
OL,5,
OL,6,FI also think that spoken announcements
OL,7,Fare the best way of ensuring Ofcom
OL,8,Fcompliance warnings are given. Yes, you
OL,9,Fcan argue for captions or generic
OL,10,Frecorded announcements on violence or
OL,11,Fstrong language. But I prefer to hear
OL,12,Fthem integrated into properly scripted
OL,13,Flinks.
OL,15,FOf course, I suppose I'm really arguing
OL,16,Fthat announcers are needed on the main
OL,17,FBBC channels. I can't pretend that the
OL,18,Fsame principled arguments should apply
OL,19,Fto all the other channels, especially
OL,20,Fthe smaller ones.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
