OL,3,GOPINIONCLive announcers: an essential
OL,4,Cpart of PSB channels
OL,5,
OL,6,FI've argued in the past that the range
OL,7,Fof voices used in modern BBC continuity
OL,8,Fmay have widened too much. I stand by
OL,9,Fthat. Diversity should not mean
OL,10,Fanything goes and undermines the role
OL,11,Fof skilled announcers with good voices
OL,12,Flike Duncan Newmarch.
OL,14,FI can also accept that having a live
OL,15,Fannouncer on duty at all times `
OL,16,Fincluding during Breakfast or the
OL,17,Fdaytime News Channel simulcast ` was
OL,18,Fwasteful.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
