OL,3,GOPINIONCLive announcers: an essential
OL,4,Cpart of PSB channels
OL,5,
OL,6,FPerhaps the efficiency in the BBC
OL,7,Fnations ` where the announcer is also
OL,8,Fthe transmission director ` should
OL,9,Foffer inspiration?
OL,11,FBut if anyone very seriously proposes
OL,12,Faxing announcers on the main BBC
OL,13,Fchannels, I'll happily join the fight
OL,14,Fto save them.
OL,16,FModern announcers are not the legacy of
OL,17,FSylvia Peters. They are an essential
OL,18,Fpart of the grammar of a public service
OL,19,Fbroadcaster.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
